gance","tag-manners-adab","tag-silence","tag-speech-al-qawl","tag-warning-al-nudhr"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-9J2","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":40190,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/05\/19\/spread-salaam-of-allah\/","url_meta":{"origin":37388,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Salaam: Spread peace of Allah on the earth","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 19, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, peace is one of the names of Allah Exalted that He has placed upon the earth, so spread peace between yourselves.\u201d Source: al-Adab al-Mufrad lil-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 989 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0633\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34101,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/04\/06\/allah-loves-concessions\/","url_meta":{"origin":37388,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Rukhsa: Allah loves believers taking His concessions","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 6, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, Allah loves for you to take His concessions, just as He loves you to fulfill His edicts.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Ibn H\u0323ibba\u0304n 354 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Arna\u2019ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0633\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":22096,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/02\/27\/rahmah-sheep-slaughter\/","url_meta":{"origin":37388,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Mercy: Have mercy on the sheep, do not slaughter","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 27, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Qurra ibn Iyas reported: A man said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, I would have slaughtered a sheep but I had mercy on it.\u201d The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cIf you had mercy on the sheep, Allah will have mercy on you twice.\u201d Source: al-Adab\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":24554,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/03\/27\/sadaqah-people-all-deen-adyan\/","url_meta":{"origin":37388,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Sadaqah: Giving charity to people of all religions","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 27, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, used to order charity only for the people of Islam, until this verse was revealed, \u201cIt is not upon you to guide them, for Allah guides whom He wills. Whatever you spend of good is for yourselves, not spending\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37533,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/12\/15\/sunnah-like-quran\/","url_meta":{"origin":37388,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Sunnah: The Prophet\u2019s commands are like Allah\u2019s commands","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 15, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Miqdam ibn Ma\u2019dikarib reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, what the Messenger of Allah has forbidden is like what Allah has forbidden.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2664 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u200c\u0627\u0644\u0652\u0645\u0650\u0642\u0652\u062f\u064e\u0627\u0645\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0645\u064e\u0639\u0652\u062f\u0650\u064a\u0643\u064e\u0631\u0650\u0628\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":26202,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/04\/13\/dua-allah-shy-empty-handed\/","url_meta":{"origin":37388,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Allah shy to turn away a sincere prayer","author":"Ab